    "%lld 个计划" : {

    },
    "• 分享导出：仅当你主动使用“导出”功能时，数据才会通过系统导出面板离开应用。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• Export sharing: Data leaves the app only when you actively use the \"Export\" feature via the system export panel."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• 分享匯出：僅當你主動使用「匯出」功能時，資料才會透過系統匯出面板離開應用。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "• 数据存储：账单、卡片、积分等数据全部保存在你的设备本地，我们不上传任何个人数据。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• Data storage: Bills, cards, points, and other data are stored locally on your device. We do not upload any personal data."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• 資料儲存：帳單、卡片、積分等資料全部保存在你的裝置本機，我們不會上傳任何個人資料。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "• 更新前建议使用“全部数据导出”进行备份！！！（重要）。" : {

    },
    "• 更新后首次打开可能需要短暂时间完成数据整理。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• After updating, the first launch may take a short time to finish organizing data."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• 更新後首次開啟可能需要短暫時間完成資料整理。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "• 权限使用：相机、相册、通知等权限仅在对应功能使用时申请，可在系统设置中随时关闭。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• Permissions: Camera, photo library, notifications, and other permissions are requested only when needed, and can be turned off anytime in Settings."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• 權限使用：相機、相簿、通知等權限僅在對應功能使用時申請，可在系統設定中隨時關閉。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "• 网络请求：应用可能会为获取汇率、下载卡面等功能访问网络，仅下载必要参数。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• Network requests: The app may access the network to fetch exchange rates or download card art, and only downloads the necessary data."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• 網路請求：應用可能會為取得匯率、下載卡面等功能存取網路，僅下載必要資料。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "• 若更新后出现应用闪退或异常的情况请删除应用，重新下载并导入之前备份的数据" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• If the app crashes or behaves abnormally after updating, please delete it, reinstall, and import your previous backup."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• 若更新後出現應用閃退或異常情況，請刪除應用、重新下載並匯入先前備份的資料。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "• 若问题仍存在，请联系开发者协助排查。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• If the issue persists, please contact the developer for assistance."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• 若問題仍存在，請聯絡開發者協助排查。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
